  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Building from Source</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">EmulatR is a CMake project built with MSVC (C++20). The build tree produces <text styleclass="Code Example">Emulatr.exe</text> under <text styleclass="Code Example">out/build/&lt;config&gt;/</text>, with the two configurations in active use being <text styleclass="Code Example">release</text> and <text styleclass="Code Example">relwithdebinfo</text> (the latter is the day-to-day debug / profiling build).</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">General shape of a build (exact preset and generator names to be confirmed):</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"># configure</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">cmake --preset &lt;preset&gt; # [TODO: confirm preset name]</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"># build (RelWithDebInfo is the standard working build)</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">cmake --build --preset &lt;preset&gt; --config RelWithDebInfo</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"># resulting binary</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">./out/build/relwithdebinfo/Emulatr.exe</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">[TODO: confirm and document the exact configure / build commands, the CMake generator, and any dependency provisioning (for example Qt and spdlog acquisition) for a clean checkout.]</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic; color:#000000;">Note: the diagnostic build flag</text> <text styleclass="Code Example">EMULATR_MEMDIAG</text> <text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic; color:#000000;">is a CMake option, not a runtime variable, and must stay OFF for normal use -- its per-instruction logging imposes roughly a 900x slowdown.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
